    "spell_type": "spell",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "text": "You create an area of bright light. Creatures with light blindness that are blinded by radiant field and remain in the area must attempt a Fortitude save at the start of their turns. On a failure, a creature remains blinded for 1 round; this is an incapacitation effect. This spell also suppresses magical darkness of your radiant field spell\u2019s rank or lower.",
